103
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:33,000
They are already ready.

104
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:33,560
Okay.

105
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,160
I'll check how the cooking is going.

106
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:35,520
Okay.

107
00:06:36,960 --> 00:06:37,360
Ma Rong,

108
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:38,800
go help her.

109
