115
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,880
In four hours,

116
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:58,320
she spent over a hundred qian.

117
00:06:58,680 --> 00:06:59,040
Look,

118
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:00,760
she bought all these things.

119
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:03,560
How much can the Magistrate earn?

120
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:05,200
