121
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:06,120
With painstaking effort.

122
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,400
You are thinking too much.

123
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:09,840
What belongs to the Magistrate

124
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:11,080
belongs to Miss Cao.

125
00:07:12,520 --> 00:07:14,600
In the future, we might have to
change our way

126
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:15,440
of addressing Miss Cao.

127
00:07:16,760 --> 00:07:17,840
What do you mean?

128
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,040
Recently, the Magistrate

129
00:07:19,320 --> 00:07:20,760
has gone out
to hunt wild geese every day.

130
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:22,680
I guess he is planning

131
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:25,120
to formally propose to Miss Cao

132
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:26,440
and hold a formal wedding.

133
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:29,720
Really well-intentioned.

134
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,880
The Magistrate really wants to marry her?

135
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:46,800
Effortlessly.

136
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:51,960
It's quite fat.

137
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:01,800
Heiyan is more and more outrageous.

138
00:08:02,280 --> 00:08:03,360
Previously, it was Diao Xiaoguan.

139
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,600
Now they've sent us a wild goose.

140
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:05,840
What do they mean?

141
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:06,920
After a long search,

142
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:08,920
we only found out that Heiyan
infiltrated all the gangs.

143
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:10,600
We can find nothing else.

144
00:08:10,840 --> 00:08:11,920
They don't trade

145
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:13,040
or gather.

146
00:08:13,280 --> 00:08:14,840
They just occasionally mess around

147
00:08:14,840 --> 00:08:15,680
or kill someone.

148
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:18,320
I still feel they are elusive.

149
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,320
Magistrate,

150
00:08:19,640 --> 00:08:20,760
can these people

151
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,520
be targeting you?

152
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:25,720
We know nothing now.

153
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:27,640
How many people

154
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:28,720
they have,

155
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:29,920
where they are staying,

156
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,280
and what their purpose is?

157
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:33,440
The only thing we can be sure of is

158
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,760
that there is one person

159
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:36,960
behind all this.

160
00:08:38,560 --> 00:08:39,560
On the day of the new moon,

161
00:08:39,760 --> 00:08:41,080
this man may appear.

162
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:43,920
How do you know that?

163
00:08:46,040 --> 00:08:47,680
The leader of the Green Dragon Gang

164
00:08:47,760 --> 00:08:48,960
we took down last month

165
00:08:49,160 --> 00:08:50,600
was also controlled by Heiyan.

166
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:53,440
According to one of his men,
Chen Xiaoyun,

167
00:08:53,920 --> 00:08:56,000
he had seen the leader of Heiyan

168
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:57,800
meeting the leaders of the gangs

169
00:08:58,320 --> 00:09:00,480
in a wood.

170
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:02,120
This wood

171
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:03,640
is their meeting place.

172
00:09:04,280 --> 00:09:05,360
They meet

173
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:07,000
on the day of the new moon every time.

174
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:09,600
The day of the new moon.

175
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:11,760
Isn't tomorrow the day of the new moon?

176
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:12,960
Magistrate, shall we...

177
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:13,520
No.

178
00:09:13,920 --> 00:09:14,440
Why?

179
00:09:14,760 --> 00:09:16,000
It's not easy to have a clue.

180
00:09:17,560 --> 00:09:18,840
Chen Xiaoyun?

181
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:23,280
First,

182
00:09:23,920 --> 00:09:25,800
we don't know whether his words

183
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,520
are true or not.

184
00:09:28,400 --> 00:09:29,000
Second,

185
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:30,320
Heiyan and we

186
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:32,160
go way back.

187
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:35,040
They never let us get

188
00:09:35,680 --> 00:09:37,720
such a clear clue.

189
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,560
Heiyan can't

190
00:09:39,560 --> 00:09:41,120
contact him only.

191
00:09:41,160 --> 00:09:42,600
Now, we finally got a clue.

192
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:43,680
We should continue to investigate.

193
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:45,280
Solving cases

194
00:09:45,680 --> 00:09:46,600
doesn't mean taking risks.

195
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:48,680
Taking such a risk

196
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:50,400
is not bravery,

197
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:52,080
but stupidity.

198
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:52,600
I...

199
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:54,120
Stop here.

200
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:55,760
Don't mention it

201
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:57,520
