202
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:04,840
Why didn't you say something?

203
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:06,680
Wasn't the clue provided by you?

204
00:10:08,640 --> 00:10:10,520
When can you stop being stupid?

205
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:14,800
I'll get the wild goose ready.

206
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:20,080
Yeah, good for you.

207
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:27,960
You are busy?

208
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:29,600
You are back.

209
00:10:32,920 --> 00:10:34,440
These are what you bought on the street?

210
00:10:36,280 --> 00:10:38,120
The white bag contains
what I bought for you.

211
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:47,320
Gloves?

212
00:10:50,760 --> 00:10:51,720
In autumn,

213
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:53,440
winds are rampant in Lanfang County.

214
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:55,200
When you hunt wild geese,

215
00:10:55,560 --> 00:10:56,680
you use a bow,

216
00:10:56,760 --> 00:10:57,920
and your hands are exposed.

217
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:58,800
I'm afraid they will get cold.

218
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:01,040
You'll need the gloves.

219
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:02,120
How do you know

220
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:03,800
I went to hunt wild geese?

221
00:11:04,520 --> 00:11:05,920
