222
00:11:06,680 --> 00:11:07,800
and you have goose feathers
on the soles of your shoes.

223
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:09,840
I've been with you for so long,

224
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:11,280
so I've been influenced.

225
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:13,040
I've learned something.

226
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:18,840
I told Hong Liang

227
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:20,360
not to tell you.

228
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:22,320
Is hunting wild geese a taboo?

229
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:24,800
Why can't you tell me?

230
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:28,120
I just wanted to wait

231
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:30,040
until everything worked out

232
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:31,280
before I told you.

233
00:11:34,680 --> 00:11:35,720
"Work" means to enhance.

234
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:37,040
"Out" indicates reality.

235
00:11:38,040 --> 00:11:39,080
"To work out"

236
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:41,160
is to enhance reality.

237
00:11:42,280 --> 00:11:44,080
I'm already very satisfied
with the reality.

238
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:46,200
After all,

239
00:11:46,360 --> 00:11:48,040
no one can predict the future.

240
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:49,880
Just seize the moment.

241
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:15,720
Well,

242
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:17,800
