245
00:12:25,880 --> 00:12:27,200
Is there anyone

246
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:28,440
doing anything productive in this house?

247
00:12:29,400 --> 00:12:30,840
My biggest business now

248
00:12:31,040 --> 00:12:32,800
is to accompany this Miss Cao
who is of unknown origin

249
00:12:32,800 --> 00:12:34,840
to stroll around every day.

250
00:12:35,800 --> 00:12:37,040
