in the room all day long.

253
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:42,640
What are you talking about?

254
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:44,480
All these years, Miss Cao

255
00:12:44,480 --> 00:12:46,040
has never troubled you with anything.

256
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:48,600
You won't even do her a little favor?

257
00:12:49,040 --> 00:12:49,920
If you are unwilling to go,

258
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:50,880
I'll go next time.

259
00:12:52,280 --> 00:12:54,560
Did she cast a spell on you?

260
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:56,040
First, Magistrate Di.

261
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:56,960
Then, Mr. Hong.

262
00:12:56,960 --> 00:12:58,200
Now it's you, right?

263
00:12:58,680 --> 00:13:00,040
What spell?

264
00:13:02,400 --> 00:13:03,920
You mustn't make baseless accusations.

265
00:13:04,640 --> 00:13:06,120
After Miss Cao came,

266
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:08,880
