584
00:35:58,000 --> 00:36:00,480
has happened in Qingchuan.

585
00:36:00,600 --> 00:36:01,960
Just rumors.

586
00:36:02,560 --> 00:36:03,560
Let's wait and see.

587
00:36:07,800 --> 00:36:08,560
Commander Xiao,

588
00:36:09,040 --> 00:36:10,440
in broad daylight,

589
00:36:11,230 --> 00:36:13,640
a few strangers died on the street.

590
00:36:14,840 --> 00:36:16,230
Is this just gonna go away?

591
00:36:18,320 --> 00:36:19,480
Magistrate Di,

592
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:21,920
you are the Magistrate
of Lanfang County.

593
00:36:21,960 --> 00:36:24,440
I am the intermediate military officer
of Qingchuan.

594
00:36:25,840 --> 00:36:27,080
I don't need you

595
00:36:28,230 --> 00:36:30,080
to teach me what to do.

596
00:36:32,710 --> 00:36:33,670
Don't take it

597
00:36:35,270 --> 00:36:36,480
personally.

598
00:36:38,120 --> 00:36:39,040
Magistrate Di,

599
00:36:40,000 --> 00:36:41,200
is there anything else

600
00:36:41,790 --> 00:36:42,960
I can do

601
00:36:44,080 --> 00:36:45,800
for you?

602
00:36:49,120 --> 00:36:50,560
Please issue

603
00:36:50,600 --> 00:36:51,560
an identity certificate

604
00:36:51,640 --> 00:36:53,640
for me.

605
00:36:54,440 --> 00:36:55,160
The name is

606
00:36:55,560 --> 00:36:56,400
Lin Muzhi.

607
00:36:56,680 --> 00:36:57,600
From Ganzhou.

608
00:36:58,280 --> 00:36:59,120
The occupation

609
00:37:01,160 --> 00:37:01,840
is a healer.

610
00:37:03,840 --> 00:37:05,240
Who is that man who was shouting

611
00:37:05,360 --> 00:37:07,760
for money in the street just now?

612
00:37:09,000 --> 00:37:09,520
He is

613
00:37:10,320 --> 00:37:11,160
called Wei Sheng.

614
00:37:11,760 --> 00:37:13,560
He is the boss of Green Bird Inn.

615
00:37:14,680 --> 00:37:15,640
Wei Sheng.

616
00:37:16,280 --> 00:37:17,880
Wei Sheng is a miser.

617
00:37:18,680 --> 00:37:19,920
Half a month ago,

618
00:37:20,480 --> 00:37:22,920
his wife ran away
with a guest in the inn.

619
00:37:23,440 --> 00:37:25,080
He curses her loudly every day,

620
00:37:25,080 --> 00:37:26,400
saying she is faithless.

621
00:37:27,400 --> 00:37:29,360
Wei Sheng is not a decent guy, either.

622
00:37:29,640 --> 00:37:30,520
I think

623
00:37:30,680 --> 00:37:32,000
it makes sense his wife

624
00:37:32,240 --> 00:37:33,240
ran off with someone else.

625
00:37:34,760 --> 00:37:36,040
He has a daughter named Wei.

626
00:37:36,560 --> 00:37:37,840
She is really pitiful.

627
00:37:38,880 --> 00:37:39,520
Thank you.

628
00:37:52,100 --> 00:37:54,700
[Wei]

629
00:38:04,680 --> 00:38:05,960
Thank you for today.

630
00:38:07,200 --> 00:38:07,920
Are you staying?

631
00:38:08,560 --> 00:38:09,000
Yes.

632
00:38:10,400 --> 00:38:11,320
Follow me.

633
00:38:15,920 --> 00:38:16,320
Boss,

634
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:17,000
chalk it up to me.

635
00:38:18,200 --> 00:38:18,560
Let's go.

636
00:38:31,480 --> 00:38:32,200
Boss.

637
00:38:35,680 --> 00:38:36,240
Boss.

638
00:38:36,860 --> 00:38:40,020
[Wei Sheng]

639
00:38:40,320 --> 00:38:41,160
Are you staying?

640
00:38:43,320 --> 00:38:43,880
How long will you stay?

641
00:38:45,200 --> 00:38:46,040
As long

642
00:38:46,080 --> 00:38:46,960
as it is necessary.

643
00:38:48,640 --> 00:38:49,880
Your identity certificate, please.

644
00:38:57,160 --> 00:38:58,160
Healer?

645
00:39:02,720 --> 00:39:03,240
Come on.

646
00:39:04,480 --> 00:39:05,200
Brat,

647
00:39:05,520 --> 00:39:06,760
take the guest to his room.

648
00:39:07,640 --> 00:39:08,440
Follow me.

649
00:39:17,280 --> 00:39:18,240
You don't look

650
00:39:18,240 --> 00:39:20,040
like his daughter.

651
00:39:20,440 --> 00:39:21,800
I'm not.

652
00:39:25,200 --> 00:39:26,400
I'm a handyman.

653
00:39:26,880 --> 00:39:28,040
I do the cleaning, cook,

654
00:39:28,520 --> 00:39:29,400
clean the rooms,

655
00:39:29,840 --> 00:39:30,640
and everything else.

656
00:39:31,280 --> 00:39:32,520
Isn't he your father?

657
00:39:34,120 --> 00:39:35,000
Foster father.

658
00:39:35,960 --> 00:39:37,960
He seems to have a load on his mind.

659
00:39:37,960 --> 00:39:39,040
He has no heart.

660
00:39:51,080 --> 00:39:51,600
You...

661
00:39:52,080 --> 00:39:53,200
You have too many questions.

662
00:39:56,000 --> 00:39:56,880
Is there

663
00:39:57,240 --> 00:39:58,360
a bathhouse in this place?

664
00:39:59,600 --> 00:40:00,320
Do you want to take a bath?

665
00:40:01,040 --> 00:40:02,000
I've traveled a long way

666
00:40:02,080 --> 00:40:03,040
and I'm travel-stained.

667
00:40:03,280 --> 00:40:04,680
I have to take a bath anyway.

668
00:40:05,240 --> 00:40:07,400
You rich people are so picky.

669
00:40:08,920 --> 00:40:10,120
Do I look

670
00:40:10,120 --> 00:40:11,800
like a rich man?

671
00:40:13,360 --> 00:40:14,000
I am

672
00:40:14,480 --> 00:40:15,840
a healer.

673
00:40:15,840 --> 00:40:17,400
I don't care what you do.

674
00:40:26,600 --> 00:40:27,720
The bathhouse is downstairs.

675
00:40:28,720 --> 00:40:29,240
Also,

676
00:40:29,960 --> 00:40:31,680
don't let other people
know you are rich.

677
00:40:32,120 --> 00:40:32,920
In Qingchuan,

678
00:40:33,280 --> 00:40:34,160
don't show your wealth.

679
00:40:48,480 --> 00:40:49,200
There are people inside.

680
00:40:52,640 --> 00:40:53,360
A private bathhouse?

681
00:40:53,640 --> 00:40:54,400
Get lost!

682
00:40:56,440 --> 00:40:57,600
Can't you hear me?

683
00:40:57,720 --> 00:40:58,800
Get lost!

684
00:40:59,880 --> 00:41:01,400
Don't be rude.

685
00:41:01,920 --> 00:41:03,000
Let him come in.

686
00:41:09,700 --> 00:41:11,060
[Miss Shiyi]

687
00:41:11,080 --> 00:41:11,920
Please.

688
00:41:21,560 --> 00:41:22,600
The home guard

689
00:41:22,600 --> 00:41:23,640
should be disciplined.

690
00:41:24,200 --> 00:41:25,800
Sorry for the rudeness.

691
00:41:27,760 --> 00:41:28,440
It doesn't matter.

692
00:41:30,200 --> 00:41:30,840
Sir,

693
00:41:32,040 --> 00:41:32,840
what's your name?

